title: Ellen McIlwaine - The Real/Everybody Needs It - 1995 [flac]
description:
Ellen McIlwaine - The Real/Everybody Needs it - 1995 [flac]

One of the most amazing and energetic slide guitarists ever onstage, Ellen played with Jimi Hendrix and Jack Bruce and has had a fifty-year solo career playing originals and covering artists as diverse as Cream, Fats Domino, Isaac Hayes, and Stevie Wonder. This is a 1995 CD re-release combining two of her earlier LPs.
